dc_title_s: West Indies, the Bahamas, Great Exuma Island, Elizabeth Harbour and approaches (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From U.S. charts to 1985." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Insets: A. Elizabeth Harbour. Scale 1:25,000 -- B. Georgetown. Scale 1:10,000. Includes compilation diagram and tidal information. Map no.26286 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
